# Veebirakenduste turvalisus tundide märkmed

## Ressursid
- https://hashcat.net/hashcat/
- https://towardsdatascience.com/logarithms-exponents-in-complexity-analysis-b8071979e847
- https://www.tunnelsup.com/hash-analyzer/
